    "However, it cannot devise comprehensive optimization plans for specific drugs (Fig. 6).Metabolic activity optimization encompasses optimization strategies aimed at enhancing the metabolic stability of compounds, prolonging drug action duration in the body, increasing exposure within the body, reducing compound clearance rates, and improving bioavailability.",
